<p>The 1st Company lost heavily most of these Chaps were either drowned or smothered in the mud really Mother you can't imagine what it is like.<br/>Well Mother you will think the first part of this letter is a bit rough well my mate just brought in a drop of Old Scotch and it has made me a little merry, and it is just beginning to wear</p>
